high_descs: Grab the newspaper off the loveseat.
Walk to the lamp on your right.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper under the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the chair containing a newspaper.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Turn right and walk to the floor lamp to the left of the blue sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the arm chair ahead, to your right.
Pick up the newspaper, on the seat of the arm chair.
Turn to your right and go to the lamp in the left corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Turn the living room lamp on.
